description: Welcome to 8 Lovis Street, a charming single-family home in the heart of South Boston offering a generous amount of living space. Enjoy the oversized primary suite with a large closet, a sun-drenched living area, and a large eat-in kitchen featuring granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. The private backyard provides an ideal spot for relaxing and entertaining. This home was once converted to a one-bedroom, but is still on public record as a two-bedroom with plenty of potential to update the layout to meet your needs. In an ideal location in Southie, this is a fantastic opportunity to skip the HOA and live comfortably in one of Boston's most sought-after neighborhoods.
